# Technical Specification: Wearable Integration for SafeFloor Industrial IoT Safety Platform

**Document Version:** 1.1 (Expansion from v1.0)  
**Author:** Senior Technical Architect, Meridian Systems  
**Date:** [Current Date]  
**Project Phase:** Module Expansion (9 months into 14-month engagement)  
**Client:** AmeriSteel Manufacturing  
**Overview:** This specification extends the AI safety monitoring platform to integrate wearable smart badges for individual worker safety. Wearables provide real-time location tracking via Ultra-Wideband (UWB) positioning, proximity alerts for heavy equipment and hazmat zones, biometric monitoring (heart rate and skin temperature) for heat stress detection, and cumulative noise exposure tracking against OSHA Permissible Exposure Limits (PEL, e.g., 90 dBA for 8 hours). Fatigue detection triggers on thresholds combining elevated heart rate and reduced movement variability, routing recommendations for mandatory rest breaks to shift supervisors.  

Integration builds on the existing hybrid cloud architecture (Azure IoT Hub with on-premises edge processing). Data privacy is maintained per client policy (e.g., anonymized worker IDs, consent-based tracking). Scalability supports 2,200 workers across 3 shifts, with peak wearable data rates of 1,000 updates/second. All components ensure low-latency alerts (<2 seconds for proximity warnings) and compliance with OSHA standards.

## 1. Data Models

Data models use JSON schemas, extending the existing sensor schemas for consistency. Timestamps are in ISO 8601 (UTC). Wearable data is stored in the time-series database (InfluxDB) with worker-anonymized identifiers.

### 1.1 Wearable Data Schema
Represents raw inputs from smart badges.

```json
{
  "$schema": "http://json-schema.org/draft-07/schema#",
  "type": "object",
  "properties": {
    "workerId": { "type": "string", "description": "Anonymized ID (e.g., 'WRK-ANON-1234')" },
    "deviceId": { "type": "string", "description": "Badge serial (e.g., 'BADGE-001')" },
    "timestamp": { "type": "string", "format": "date-time" },
    "location": {
      "type": "object",
      "properties": {
        "zone": { "type": "string", "enum": ["ZoneA", "ZoneB", "ZoneC", "..."] },
        "coordinates": { "type": "array", "items": { "type": "number" }, "minItems": 3, "maxItems": 3 }  // [x, y, z] via UWB
      },
      "required": ["zone", "coordinates"]
    },
    "proximity": {
      "type": "array",
      "items": {
        "type": "object",
        "properties": {
          "entity": { "type": "string", "enum": ["HeavyEquipment", "HazmatZone"] },
          "distance": { "type": "number", "description": "Meters" },
          "alert": { "type": "boolean", "description": "True if within threshold (e.g., <5m)" }
        }
      }
